<div class="overflow-hidden">
  <div class="relative max-w-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:max-w-7xl">

    <div class="relative my-12 lg:mt-16 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8 lg:items-start">
      <div class="relative">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 tracking-tight sm:text-4xl mt-8">
            Le topo qui tient dans votre poche.
          </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-gray-500">
          L'appli Boolder est votre compagnon idéal pour vos sorties grimpe à Fontainebleau :
        </p>

        <dl class="mt-10 space-y-10">

          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-500 text-white">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                Carte géolocalisée
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                Repérez-vous facilement dans la forêt grâce au GPS et à la boussole.
              </dd>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-500 text-white">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                Des milliers de voies avec photos
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                Trouvez facilement les voies qui vous conviennent.
              </dd>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-500 text-white">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 16a4 4 0 01-.88-7.903A5 5 0 1115.9 6L16 6a5 5 0 011 9.9M9 19l3 3m0 0l3-3m-3 3V10" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                Mode hors-ligne
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                L'appli fonctionne même si vous passez en mode avion.
              </dd>
            </div>
          </div>


          <div class="flex justify-center py-8">
          <%= link_to "#" do %>
            <%= render 'svg/app_store_badge', height: 40*2, width: 126.5*2 %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 -mx-4 relative lg:mt-0" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="relative">
            

            <video autoplay loop muted width="301" src="/videos/demo.en.mov" class="absolute bg-gray-900 h-full" style="top:15px; left:18px; height: 648px">

                <%= image_tag 'app-screenshot.png', class: "relative mx-auto", width: "300" %>
            </video>

            <%= image_tag 'iphone-frame.png', class: "relative mx-auto absolute top-0 left-0", width: "336" %>
          
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


  </div>
</div>

